**Step 2 — Open and edit `.gitignore` in VS Code
```
# Virtual environment
venv/

# Environment variables / API keys
.env

# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# VS Code settings
.vscode/

# Jupyter notebooks checkpoints
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Distribution / packaging
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/